ic to C(K_2).\n  These results are applied to the isomorphic classification of some spaces of\ncompact operators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Nov 2010 22:42:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Jul 2011 02:40:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
