vely small $\\beta\\ge1$, in probability\nfor moderate sized $\\beta$ and in distribution when $\\beta$ is large.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2010 09:18:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-16"}
