olutionary and pulsation models of these\nstars, and should be taken into account in the calibration of the Cepheid\ndistance scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Nov 2010 13:57:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-01-26"}
